~ start
if GlobalVariables.haskey == false: 
	do get_tree().call_group("Player", "item_pose")
	do sfx_success()
	I got a key! It's unlabeled though, I dunno what it goes to. I guess I'll just have to try anything with a functional keyhole.
	do get_tree().call_group("key", "invis")
	set GlobalVariables.haskey = true
do CutsceneManager.endcutscene()
=> END